## Article 10 (Suspension of Services)

1. The Company may temporarily suspend services for reasons such as maintenance, replacement, or breakdown of information and communication equipment, or communication disconnection.

2. The Company compensates users or third parties for damages arising from temporary service suspension as above, except when the Company proves no intent or negligence.

